Detailed Description

cvmx_hna_hnc1_ram2#

This address space allows read-only access to HNC1 RAM2 for diagnostic use. It is defined here to contain 64 words (16 RAM lines) for basic DV testing, but the actual address space spans the entire RAM1, 512 lines.
